Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:06.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野 你和30年前相比一点没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:11.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是么 你想说的不是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:16.31,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治现在做什么工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:19.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:23.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:28.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你代替我去调查一下礼治的住处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后  把那个东西  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:36.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,想要把它要回来 我的攻略笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:40.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:43.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:47.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我想要采访发生在你身上的所有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:57.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,1986年 我们终于高中毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,找到了自己的目的的高野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:03.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的考上了时尚相关的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:06.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后 高考失败的我和木户
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:11.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,迎来了临近入学考试的复习生的冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:52.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,少一个劲儿升级了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:21.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:27.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊 哦 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个洛特的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在哪呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:36.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 我踢飞你哟 诶 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:38.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有洛特的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就没法证明我是洛特的子孙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,洛特洛特的 你烦不烦 我马上就快要考试了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是么 好吧 我明白了 那 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:48.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 马上打木户的电话给我问问他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户现在也是在拼命追赶中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,他不玩游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 KID也很薄情寡义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,突然就不来店里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,托他的福  我们的店也快完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:05.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道快不行了就赶紧工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在大家都在玩《勇者斗恶龙》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,而且 今天是第二季的发表日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:14.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不来玩这种街机游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:18.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 金属史莱姆 啊 跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:22.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,金属史莱姆很害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哈 所以 它出来了就赶快逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:37.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我在要做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:51.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 不好了 不好了 礼治 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 不好了 礼治 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:56.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 看看这个 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,跟着滚轴公主在客栈住宿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,主人这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,（-早上好，昨晚上真是太棒了 -欢迎您再来）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是服了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我想到是游戏之前都没怎么注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,想不到做得这么细致呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么 为什么 生气了 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:20.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我三个小时的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老实去找 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,复活的咒语吧 哦 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊 额
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:11.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野要是感冒了的话怎么办啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,OK 已经全部结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 OK OK 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:58.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,勇者斗恶龙2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:50.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:53.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个 怎么玩好呢 先走走看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:03.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦 出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,勇者之泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是勇者斗恶龙2吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,借爸爸玩一下 借爸爸玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,呐 礼治 呐呐  借爸爸玩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊  喂喂  又是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:17.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  王子到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,已经忍不住了   就一会儿 总之借我玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会帮你找出王子的 借我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你想想是什么让你落榜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 借给我借给我   你在干嘛 在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.87,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等下 等下 等等 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的  这个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:41.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不好 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要使意思畅通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:50.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就必须了解句子结构
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这个分词语法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么回事 今早就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:54.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,山元爷爷 你看到木户不  KID
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:58.39,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就是总和我在一起的 带着圆圆的眼镜 -刚才还在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.99,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,错过了啊   谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 木户来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:13.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是啊   抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.87,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 二者大叔     礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:45.87,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,KID 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,把了不得的东西塞给我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个游戏是个怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:57.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕的袭击我们复考生的心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我找了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就让我们把力量合在一起 并肩战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:36.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治 像勇者斗恶龙2里头的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:41.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谜语暗示  地图的大小 怪物的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:46.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,全部都远远超过勇者斗恶龙1  确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:49.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.83,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这里要小组合作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:55.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,并肩战斗 即使一秒 也要快点打倒魔王——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:58.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,回去继续学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:04.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不行   不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这为什么是错误啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:18.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不知道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你是路痴吗  死路痴 老是在关键时候掉链子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也不用全部扔掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,错都错了还留着做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我只是让你去那儿确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:32.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你要怎么补偿我们今天六个小时的人生 啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:36.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么补偿……我才想说这句呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋 你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,去开门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:52.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野 嗯 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:58.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治君 高野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:04.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊   勇者斗恶龙2啊  你们果然在玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:08.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个错了  我弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:12.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这不是｢ぬれぞ｣吗    不是｢めれぞ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  你们加把油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:34.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,｢ぬ｣和｢め｣弄错了 又不是外行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野玩过勇者斗恶龙1吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,话说 好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:42.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,都怪这貂皮大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,实在热得受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这下终于自在点儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:09.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,像我这么大还在玩游戏的女人已经没了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以才一直游离不定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:14.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个   你们   打算通关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:17.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是那么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:21.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是比1难很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:26.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那我来帮你们升级
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间 你们去学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:35.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 我在这方面还是很能努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:39.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 放心吧 我不会先前进的 高野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:44.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,请你们在三次元的世界好好战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:02.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,（进击的礼治）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,（进击的木户）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,加守防备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,（礼治背住了新单词）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好 拉里发！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,Put up 推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:45.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等等 礼治 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:50.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,挺着 make no difference
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:54.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,Make no difference 随便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:58.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇哇（礼治升级了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:34.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了 罗恩达路奇亚的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:37.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,总共7层
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:42.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,最大的最坏的 陷阱和怪物的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:53.15,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的好吗 礼治 明天是考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,准备通宵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:18:00.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哼 如果世界毁灭了 没有被拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,考试还算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:16.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个 这里不是一样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:19.39,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 落入陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:22.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱 哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:25.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:28.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不好吧 你们就知道说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:35.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,危险 危险 危险 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:44.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又落入陷阱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:47.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,继续 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.71,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊  杀手机关枪咒语不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.87,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 快逃 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.67,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又掉下去了 那里是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,写一下攻略 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 这儿？ 我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是你不肯思考 -不是这儿？那是这儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,看见了吗 -哎呀 都是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,吵吵闹闹的 我完全不知道在哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我是让你画地图啊 啊 为什么吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,危险 危险 危险 快逃 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:29.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,战斗啊 又死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:33.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个礼治 你看都是因为你没写在地图上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:37.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不 啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 又回到开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要还是这样 天就要亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:50.07,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:53.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:58.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎 太厉害了吧 这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:02.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,又要从刚刚升级的地方开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 金属史莱姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:20.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,打不中 它跑了 它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:22.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊啊 它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:27.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,去了 好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.83,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,罗恩达路奇亚高地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:03.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮啊 松口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:12.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,到底想要什么呢 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:18.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,Put up 推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:20.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你们升级
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:24.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,请你们在另一个世界好好战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:33.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕的袭击我们复考生的心的怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:37.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,共同努力战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:48.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:53.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,敌人很强大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:22:00.03,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个洞里的那么强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:08.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:20.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,通过勇者斗恶龙2 我们3个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:22.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,第一次实现共同目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:27.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户和我还有高野一起学到了合作的重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:30.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是通过大学考试的最后关卡
